  "text": "PCM, nevertheless, faces important challenges. It is wearable such that only about 10 7 or 10 8 writes can be performed. A PCM system would fail in days or even hours without wear-leveling or write minimization [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . PCM is slower and consumes more energy on writes than DRAM.",
